Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.35,0:00:04.75,MENarration,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Just as water flows without shape {\blur2}and wind blows without form,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.75,0:00:06.36,MENarration,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}no case can stop you from deducing the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.36,0:00:08.36,MENarration,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}People's feelings are the key to solving this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:10.40,MENarration,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I want to find out how Ran really feels!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.40,0:00:12.32,MENarration,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:13.99,MENarration,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.99,0:00:16.45,MENarration,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\t(2026,2560,\c&HF1F5F2&\4c&HF1F5F2&)}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.48,0:02:02.36,Narr,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}The old man only has 6 months left to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.80,0:02:07.00,Narr,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Well, that's what he thought he was hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:09.56,Narr,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}But he was actually just being told to stay away from alcohol for 6 months.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.13,0:02:14.65,Narr,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}The doctor, Yoshiteru Araide{\rHonorifics - Narr}-san{\r}, invited us to stay for dinner at his house.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:20.21,Narr,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}But after a short blackout, Yoshiteru{\rHonorifics - Narr}-san{\r} was found dead in the bathtub!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.67,0:02:34.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A doctor {\i1}and{\i0} a sports coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:37.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't believe me, ask Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:41.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The team I'm coaching is at Teitan High School, the same school she goes to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:44.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}T-Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.19,0:02:51.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ran went out to karate practice every evening to see {\i1}this{\i0} guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.95,0:02:54.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.29,0:02:55.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that right, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:03:00.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. You can check with the high school as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.10,0:03:02.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May I go? I've got a burn to treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.80,0:03:03.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:08.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, and you need to come to the clinic too, Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.05,0:03:10.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no use hiding it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:14.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I noticed you were limping just now,\Nlike something's wrong with your foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:15.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Foot?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.85,0:03:21.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What happened to your foot?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:27.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While I was coming downstairs in the dark, I stepped on something strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:32.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May I go help him treat everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.20,0:03:33.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:34.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:39.15,Dialogue,,10,10,0,,I got a hold of the person that Yōko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was talking to on the phone when the lights went out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.56,0:03:40.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, and...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.56,0:03:47.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She said that the time it took since Yōko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} told her the lights went out
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.13,0:03:51.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to the time she reported that the lights went on was about a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.24,0:03:56.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd like to get Yōko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to give her side of the story to ensure it matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.45,0:03:58.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.41,0:04:00.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.29,0:04:01.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I help treat everyone first, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:03.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:07.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't mind, I can assist the doctor instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:10.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty good at stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.12,0:04:12.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, you can take over for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:17.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her story matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.10,0:04:18.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only time they weren't talking
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.85,0:04:20.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was the six or seven seconds she took to answer the call waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.30,0:04:25.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So Yōko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was on the phone throughout the blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:26.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.97,0:04:28.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course I was!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:33.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, do you have a floor plan of this house?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:34.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:39.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the bathroom where your husband died.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:43.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we must be here, right? This is the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:44.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.79,0:04:47.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's the circuit breaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.38,0:04:53.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You go left from the kitchen and turn left twice, then right once...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:54.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:05:01.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the maid, left the kitchen to check the breaker
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.26,0:05:06.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,around the time you told Masae{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} about the blackout, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:06.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.85,0:05:10.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then it's odd that you were without light for a whole minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:14.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like it'd take less than 30 seconds to get to the breaker from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.18,0:05:18.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} has just started working here. She's not used to the house yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:23.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when your stepson saw that Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'d burnt her arm,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:25.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,didn't he say something like\N‘You still put up with everything'?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.45,0:05:35.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Tomoaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} took care of Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} during his clinical training at Tohto Medical School.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.63,0:05:39.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her appendix almost burst because she ignored the pain for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.47,0:05:43.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that how Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} ended up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.60,0:05:44.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.45,0:05:50.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With my mother-in-law getting on in years,\NI can't take care of this household alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:52.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I hired her as a live-in maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.14,0:05:57.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's embarrassing, really. Chiaki took care of the whole house by herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:05:59.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.09,0:06:02.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Tomoaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s late mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.65,0:06:05.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She died four years ago from a car accident, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.81,0:06:08.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems she was driving drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:13.97,Dialogue,,10,10,0,,I still can't believe it — she'd always been a light drinker, since she knew she couldn't hold her alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:18.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, where's your mother-in-law's room?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:19.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:22.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You take the stairs to the left of the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:25.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the first large room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.85,0:06:27.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An old person like her living upstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:33.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. She loves the view of the garden from that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.75,0:06:39.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I gave Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} the room next door,\Nso she could help if anything happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.78,0:06:44.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, the killer must've tried to call Yōko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} as a distraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.47,0:06:48.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While she answered the call waiting,\Nthe killer slipped past the kitchen,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:51.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,entered the bathroom,\Nand put the cord into the tub.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.95,0:06:55.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid. How would she get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:55.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:06:58.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you whispering about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.58,0:07:00.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.01,0:07:01.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.45,0:07:05.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you have everybody do what they were doing during the blackout?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:10.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, that's not a bad idea.\NWhile their memories are still fresh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.25,0:07:12.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.11,0:07:20.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're good with the bandages.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:21.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:27.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew a boy who used to get injured all the time, so I got to be an expert.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.08,0:07:29.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that was a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.77,0:07:32.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:35.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez. The {\i1}nurse{\i0} shouldn't get injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:40.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's not serious. We can just wash it and put on a plaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.91,0:07:44.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:47.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:50.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:54.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er, the Inspector's calling for everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.83,0:07:57.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it. We'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:07:57.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.86,0:07:59.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.30,0:08:01.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you hand me a plaster from that cupboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:02.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:04.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Silly me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.19,0:08:06.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What am I thinking at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.40,0:08:14.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.94,0:08:18.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The breaker should be at the end of this hallway, to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.15,0:08:21.89,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Aha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:23.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.78,0:08:26.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.47,0:08:31.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be careful! This is where Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} dropped the vase!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.08,0:08:37.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I helped her pick up the pieces.\NI felt so sorry for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.94,0:08:43.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoshiteru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} got really mad.\NHe even threatened to fire her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:48.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait a minute. That could mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.89,0:08:52.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, are you all ready? Let's get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:54.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roger. We're ready at the stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:57.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm in place, in front of the breaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.73,0:09:00.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, Takagi! Kill the breaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:01.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:04.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, could you go to the breaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.90,0:09:05.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.39,0:09:20.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,34 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.05,0:09:22.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought, it took less than a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:26.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.02,0:09:27.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you cross this garden,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.94,0:09:31.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you can get to the bathroom without sneaking past Yōko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:34.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, you don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:37.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. There was enough time for her to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:39.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:40.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you cut it out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.11,0:09:42.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haven't we told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:46.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everybody in this house had an alibi before the lights went out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.96,0:09:50.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So why keep bugging us about what happened during the blackout?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:52.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We need to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.46,0:09:52.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:59.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We just had a terrible accident, and you're amusing yourselves with your ugly theories!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.90,0:10:01.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, er...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.84,0:10:04.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have I done something wrong again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.40,0:10:06.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.40,0:10:08.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Their alibis...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.45,0:10:16.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Only one of those four people has a really solid alibi for the time of the murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:22.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Of the remaining three, one is very suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.61,0:10:27.27,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A fragment of something!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.95,0:10:30.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is this red mark blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.70,0:10:33.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And what's this weird thing stuck to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.50,0:10:37.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.42,0:10:45.01,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:46.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So that's how it happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:52.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Which means that there's only one person who could have been the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.98,0:11:01.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ten seconds, round trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:05.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So she did have the opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:09.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, the thing that we were concerned about...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.09,0:11:11.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yup. It's not even an issue...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.71,0:11:18.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't tell me, it's come?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:22.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. A light bulb just went on in my head.\NI know the truth behind the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.93,0:11:27.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you could take me to the bathroom, I'll explain everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.53,0:11:30.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My back hurts a bit, so it'd help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:31.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.05,0:11:34.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? He wants to take a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.93,0:11:36.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.15,0:11:39.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He got wet in the rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.25,0:11:44.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and he wants to see if you can really get an electric shock by using that razor in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.69,0:11:46.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's the Inspector and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.77,0:11:49.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The detectives said they\Nwere leaving for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.26,0:11:52.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way! What a shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:54.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.03,0:11:59.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'Cause Uncle Kogorō said that once he gets out of the bath,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.21,0:12:01.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he'll put on a deduction show for everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.43,0:12:06.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} really say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.38,0:12:09.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's figured out who the killer is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:13.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer? But didn't my husband die in an accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.53,0:12:16.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.35,0:12:21.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he said he wants to have a bath and collect his thoughts first, so he might be a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.92,0:12:26.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been 20 minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.27,0:12:29.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s taking a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.82,0:12:33.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of that toothbrush moustache guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:35.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.88,0:12:43.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.29,0:12:45.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:49.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. Another blackout?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.92,0:12:55.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}. Could you go take a look at the breaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:55.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:13:00.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why another blackout?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:05.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, that man said he was running an experiment in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:08.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.34,0:13:10.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.27,0:13:13.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was fast. It's already back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:15.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that was {\i1}too{\i0} fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.84,0:13:19.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:22.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:25.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the killer, aren't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.22,0:13:27.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yōko Araide{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.08,0:13:32.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yōko and the little boy have run off...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:34.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't tell me this was a trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.64,0:13:40.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-Inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.01,0:13:45.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm the killer? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:48.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just came to see if you were okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.23,0:13:51.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard you were experimenting with the razor in the bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:53.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You wanted it to look that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.91,0:13:56.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but really, you wanted to kill me because I'd figured out the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.30,0:14:00.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then pretend to have discovered my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:03.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop talking nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.44,0:14:06.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know I was talking on the phone throughout the blackout!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.42,0:14:09.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.17,0:14:14.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You created some kind of timer that could\Nshort-circuit the electricity in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.26,0:14:19.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You used that penlight to make\Nyour way here in the dark,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:25.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then dropped the razor's extension cord into\Nthe tub where your husband was bathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.22,0:14:30.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That way, when someone reset the breaker, he'd die of an electric shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.94,0:14:37.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like I said, I was on the phone with my friend the whole time the lights were out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:38.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So how could I come up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:45.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was simple. Anybody could've done it with the phone's cordless handset and a mobile phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.63,0:14:51.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unlike the phone in the kitchen,\Nthe handset is cordless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:54.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Additionally, the main phone has\Na built-in rechargeable battery
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.35,0:14:57.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that makes it usable even during blackouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:15:01.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As soon as Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} left the kitchen,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:04.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you switched receivers to the cordless handset and went to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.10,0:15:08.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You used your mobile's speed dial to phone the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:12.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pretending you had someone on call waiting,\Nyou stopped the conversation for a moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:17.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,grabbed the extension cord,\Nwhich you'd plugged in beforehand,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.43,0:15:22.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and snuck it into the tub while pointing the light at your husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.08,0:15:32.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You probably told him to be careful to make him grab hold of a handrail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.63,0:15:36.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you returned to the kitchen,\Nstill talking on the handset,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.45,0:15:40.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,switched back to the kitchen phone,\Nand waited for the lights to turn on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.10,0:15:46.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why when Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} reset the circuit, it tripped again immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.44,0:15:49.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the lights turned back on the first time, your husband,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.87,0:15:56.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,who was holding the handrail,\Nwas electrocuted, and died instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.98,0:16:00.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But anybody could've done that, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.65,0:16:01.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.70,0:16:05.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your plan was to create\Nan alibi using the phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:12.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and also to establish alibis for the others\Nby blocking the corridor to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:15.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But a problem arose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:21.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} took an extra\N30 seconds to reset the breaker,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.24,0:16:25.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,her alibi could not be established.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:31.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know why she took so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.19,0:16:33.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the {\i1}chawanmushi{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:35.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During the blackout,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:39.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} broke one of the {\i1}chawanmushi{\i0} dishes in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:46.27,Dialogue,,10,10,0,,She held it under her arm and went upstairs to hide it in her room before going to reset the breaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.26,0:16:53.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Earlier, your husband had threatened to fire her if she made another mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.31,0:16:56.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, that burn on her arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:17:01.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what caused her burn and the mark on your mother-in-law's foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.57,0:17:05.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While leaving her room in the darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.47,0:17:09.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,she stepped on a shard of the broken dish that Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} dropped in the corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:15.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s detour added\Nan extra 30 seconds to her trip,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.50,0:17:18.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and during that time,\Nthe old lady was still upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.25,0:17:21.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tomoaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} couldn't have left the kitchen,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:23.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,since Ran was hanging on to him throughout the blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.50,0:17:27.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you understand now, Yōko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.47,0:17:33.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the only person who could have committed this crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:37.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me go, Inspector! Let me into the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:39.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's currently under investigation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.50,0:17:42.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}framed{\i0} her, and you call it an investigation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:43.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.93,0:17:48.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Silly girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:53.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did she think we wouldn't notice the missing dish?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:58.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} hadn't done anything,\Nyou would never have suspected me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.06,0:18:04.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. Even if she didn't hide the dish,\NI still would have figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.59,0:18:07.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hand you held the phone in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.47,0:18:13.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} left the kitchen, you were holding the phone in your left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:18.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it was in your right hand\Nwhen the lights went back on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:24.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It gave me the idea that you might've left the phone at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.06,0:18:29.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You went to the bathroom with Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} when she discovered the body
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:31.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to make sure she wouldn't touch it and get a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.40,0:18:38.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Conan hadn't stopped Tomoaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},\Nyou were going to stop him too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.90,0:18:40.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.52,0:18:44.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiaki told me to take care of Tomoaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:49.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. Four years ago, on the night Chiaki died, she called me and said,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.64,0:18:55.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,‘Look after Tomoaki for me and make sure he doesn't turn out like my husband'.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.68,0:18:59.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the time, I didn't know what she meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:04.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I understood after I married\Nhim and found Chiaki's diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.43,0:19:09.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I learnt that my husband was a womaniser\Nwho'd chase after any woman he saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:14.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He{\i0} was the reason Chiaki began to drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:17.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He drove her to her death!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.00,0:19:18.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:22.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd like to advise you to turn yourself in as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:25.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, how kind of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.88,0:19:29.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. I'm not doing this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.79,0:19:31.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm doing this for Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.26,0:19:36.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got no idea, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:39.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You may have been the one who set up the murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.68,0:19:43.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} triggered it\Nby resetting the breaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.06,0:19:48.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Knowing that she {\i1}killed{\i0} a man\Nwill scar her for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.66,0:19:53.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the reason you didn't tell anybody the blackout was a fake...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.82,0:19:58.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. So Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} wouldn't figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:01.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.25,0:20:05.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell the police that you killed your husband by putting him in the bathtub
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:08.89,Dialogue,,10,10,0,,after drugging him and putting an electric cord connected to a timer in the tub
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:15.77,Dialogue,,10,10,0,,to give him a fatal electric shock, then removing the timer during the blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.54,0:20:20.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Basically, tell them the murder occurred during the first blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.55,0:20:25.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, if you confess in court that I asked you to say this,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.50,0:20:27.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then it'll get me and the Inspector into trouble too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.23,0:20:31.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. I'll do as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.64,0:20:37.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want to lose my human heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.60,0:22:09.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for keeping you here so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.57,0:22:10.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:13.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want you to tell your father...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.89,0:22:14.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.59,0:22:16.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.20,0:22:19.27,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.02,0:22:23.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell him I spoke too soon back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.16,0:22:25.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm willing to help him if he ever needs me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.13,0:22:27.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What was I thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.68,0:22:29.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.14,0:22:33.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know it's weird to ask you at a time like this, but if it's okay with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.95,0:22:39.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...can I borrow that hand-knitted sweater you're wearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.39,0:22:43.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}S-Sweater?
