Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.56,0:21:01.07,FreeMagicTL,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Free Magic, in its true form
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.07,0:21:06.45,FreeMagicTL,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Free Magic, what is this thing called love?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:11.54,FreeMagicTL,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Even if you're blindly searching through darkness for warmth
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.54,0:21:17.71,FreeMagicTL,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Someday you'll surely find a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.84,0:21:30.10,FreeMagicTL,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Free Magic, if love were to take form, it'd be round like an egg
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:41.44,FreeMagicTL,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Free Magic, so right now, speak your first cry in these hands
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:49.95,FreeMagicTL,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Even with faked bravery you can still be reckless
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.95,0:21:55.37,FreeMagicTL,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Free Magic, you may not have much courage now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.37,0:22:06.01,FreeMagicTL,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(0,500)}Free Magic, but I'll gather and raise it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.05,0:22:45.03,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,‘Kisaki Law Office'
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.83,0:22:49.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, so this part is like this, and then this part...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.23,0:22:52.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, where'd you get that sweater?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.15,0:22:55.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I borrowed it off a friend.\NI just love the pattern!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.85,0:22:58.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's an Aran pattern. It's difficult, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.89,0:23:01.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that part's not quite right...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.18,0:23:02.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, let me show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.31,0:23:05.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, no! I'm going to knit this myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.95,0:23:09.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine. But don't come crying to me if you{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} tan{\r}gle it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.22,0:23:13.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I can't manage it, show me how to do it with another needle!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:18.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've already knitted two sweaters for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.01,0:23:22.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sounds like you'd be better off giving a box of cakes rather than a sweater.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.12,0:23:23.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.16,0:23:26.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's been working hard lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.78,0:23:28.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You sound jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.06,0:23:31.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, now how did this bit go...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.01,0:23:35.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, those sweaters I knitted are in the way. Could you get rid of them for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.63,0:23:36.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No prob!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.79,0:23:41.96,Signs,,0,0,0,,A few days later
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.30,0:23:38.89,Phone,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an8}Hey, did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.89,0:23:41.94,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Yeah. The doc sent it to me yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.48,0:23:43.96,Phone,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}And? Did you try it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.96,0:23:46.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm wearing it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.06,0:23:47.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.44,0:23:50.87,Phone,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}What're you laughing about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.70,0:23:52.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.24,0:23:55.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said what're you laughing about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.81,0:23:57.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.78,0:24:11.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.76,0:24:13.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.43,0:24:14.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened, Sonoko-{\i1}neechan{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.65,0:24:30.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the next Conan: 'The Dying Message That Comes Back (Part I)'!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.74,0:24:35.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: The sound of fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.02,0:24:37.55,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time, we're at an ice-skating rink!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.55,0:24:40.15,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Ah, out the way, out the way, get out of the way!
